      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BILLY ME GOAT (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with five wins and two minors from 14 tries. Was out of the placings last time (28.06) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 6 lengths. Looks suited and should go close. SWEET MICHELLE (7) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (35.94) last time in a Grade 5 at Cannington. Form here is sound including three wins. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. ASTON BRADLEY (2) stuck on well last time to finish a nose back in second (27.64) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 488m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can measure up. MILITARIES (1) is in form and worth thought again.",
